tables.table_schema:
CREATE TABLE fingerprint_data (
    id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    fingerprint TEXT,
    encrypted_fingerprint TEXT,
    encryption_key TEXT
)

CREATE TABLE fingerprint_data (
  id INT PRIMARY KEY,
  fingerprint_data BYTEA,
  encrypted BOOLEAN
)

CREATE TABLE encryption_keys (
  key_id SERIAL PRIMARY KEY,
  encryption_key BYTEA
)

CREATE TABLE decryption_keys (
  key_id SERIAL PRIMARY KEY,
  decryption_key BYTEA
)

CREATE TABLE users (
  user_id SERIAL PRIMARY KEY,
  username VARCHAR(50),
  password_hash BYTEA
)

CREATE TABLE access_logs (
  log_id SERIAL PRIMARY KEY,
  user_id INT,
  access_time TIMESTAMP
)
